div.div:
Activator Handlers
- Proxy with call to throttler, then to pod
- ConcurrencyHandler (counts requests)
- TracingHandler
- RequestLogHandler
- MetricsHandler (reports latency + resp. code)
- ContextHandler (sets revId in ctx)
- ProbeHandler (return 200 OK if probe, else do nothing)
- ProbeHeaderHandler (forward Hash-Key if probe header)
- HealthCheckHandler (checks internal health from kubelet)

div.div:
Autoscaler Hierarchy
- Multiscaler is a decider and is poked when metrics from arrive activator
- Metrics from activator are also added to MetricsCollector
- Immediately poke scaler if it's 0 and has requests
- KPA Reconciler: Trigger PA => SKS, Decider, Metrics, and Scale is run
- Decider says how many pods
- Scaler does the actual scaling
